text: Write down the output of the given program. Show with dry-run in table. CLS P=1: Q=1 CALL DISP(P,Q) END SUB DISP(M,N) WHILE (N<=5) PRINT M M=M*10+N N=N+1 WEND END SUB
norm: write down the output of the given program. show with dry-run in table. cls p=1: q=1 call disp(p,q) end sub disp(m,n) while (n<=5) print m m=m*10+n n=n+1 wend end sub
